154
00:06:32.617 --> 00:06:35.718
Ću imati
denar bombona. molim.

155
00:06:40.425 --> 00:06:42.291
Hvala.

156
00:06:42.893 --> 00:06:45.027
O. moj Bože. tu su
toliko kombinacija.

157
00:06:45.029 --> 00:06:46.528
Ovo će potrajati nekoliko sati.

158
00:06:46.530 --> 00:06:48.197
Evo. daj da vidim to.

159
00:06:53.838 --> 00:06:55.771
Koliko dugo to trajati?

160
00:07:02.980 --> 00:07:05.047
Agent Ressler. riječ.
Ja ću to Aram.

161
00:07:05.049 --> 00:07:06.815
Pronašli smo SD čip.

162
00:07:06.817 --> 00:07:09.418
Aram bi trebao biti u mogućnosti koristiti ga
locirati Crna misu.

163
00:07:10.921 --> 00:07:12.721
Reven Wright...

164
00:07:13.323 --> 00:07:15.323
Mi je bio superioran i moj prijatelj.

165
00:07:15.325 --> 00:07:17.125
Pa mi se ne sviđa ova
više od tebe.

166
00:07:17.127 --> 00:07:19.027
Ali istraga
njezinu disappearance--

167
00:07:19.029 --> 00:07:20.428
